last_episode_to_air.name: How It All Ends
last_episode_to_air.overview: As Walter's situation grows dire, Sheldon and Brandon join forces in a do-or-die showdown with a supervillain. Hutch runs into trouble during a heist.

name: Jupiter's Legacy
overview: As the world's first generation of superheroes (who received their powers in the 1930s) become the revered elder guard in the present, their superpowered children struggle to live up to the legendary feats of their parents.

seasons.name: Volume 1
seasons.overview: They're the first generation of superheroes. But as they pass the torch to their children, tensions are rising — and the old rules no longer apply.

episodes.name: By Dawn's Early Light
episodes.overview: Brandon's attempt to live up to his father's high expectations suffers a blow. Sheldon's carefree life as the boss's son comes crashing down in 1929.

episodes.name: Paper and Stone
episodes.overview: Brandon and Chloe clash with their dad after the Blackstar incident. Sheldon confronts a reporter over an exposé on the family business.

episodes.name: Painting the Clouds With Sunshine
episodes.overview: Worried about Sheldon's uncharacteristic behavior, George pays him a visit. A foiled theft lands Hutch on the wrong side of a superpowered crime boss.

episodes.name: All the Devils Are Here
episodes.overview: With her partying spiraling out of control, Chloe nears rock bottom. Sheldon encounters hardship in his search for answers to the visions haunting him.

episodes.name: What's the Use?
episodes.overview: Sheldon tries to assemble a dream team for his quest into the unknown. An autopsy unearths a puzzling object that connects to Chloe's new acquaintance.

episodes.name: Cover Her Face
episodes.overview: Grace sees first-hand how the Code is affecting the younger superheroes. Tempers flare aboard the ship as Sheldon forges ahead with his expedition.

episodes.name: Omnes Pro Uno
episodes.overview: The perilous final leg of their journey pushes Sheldon's ragtag team to the brink. Walter reaches out to a questionable source to extract information.

episodes.name: How It All Ends
episodes.overview: As Walter's situation grows dire, Sheldon and Brandon join forces in a do-or-die showdown with a supervillain. Hutch runs into trouble during a heist.
